              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="slider-content text-wrapper">
                <h6>After</h6>
                <h2>Faster recovery</h2>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="next" class="next"><img src="{{ 'link-arrow-black.png' | asset_url }}" alt=""></a>

        <div class="text-wrapper">
          <h3>Sound familiar?</h3>
          <p>Turns out, swapping old blood for new blood has some pretty noticable results. We don't agree with Lance, but we see where he was coming from.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="grid__item padded">
      {{ pages.add-compression.content }}
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
